Key-Points
- Creational Pattern

Description
- This pattern provides one of the best way of creating objects
- This pattern involves a single class which is responsible to create an object
- and it also makes usre that only single object gets created.
- The class provides way to access its only object 

Advantages and When to use
- Can be used when we want to create only sinlge object and use it in many different 
locations
- Ideal for following cases
  - Classes without attributes
  - class has a read only state

Disadvantages/ Limitations

Steps to run this file
git clone
cd Singleton Pattern
tsc index.ts
node index.js
